2.1.name: wordpress/enhanced-wordpress-contactform
2.1.description:
Easy contact form, embed it in a post or page by writing the shortcode [wpcf].

Features:

  • Spam protection.
  • Shows referrer information for the person contacting you.
  • Option for user to send himself a copy of the message.

More info:

  • Enhanced WordPress Contact Form.
